reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 🎵Rollin' with Charmin: A Symphony of Softness and Strength🎵
reviews.reviewText: Ah, Charmin Ultra Strong Clean Touch Toilet Paper, the unsung hero of our daily deeds, the catcher of our...well, let’s keep things PG and say “missteps.”Let’s get to the bottom of this (pun intended). What does one look for in a TP? Softness? Strength? The ability to transform your bathroom time into an otherworldly, cloud-like experience? Charmin boasts it all, and we’re about to wipe the floor with this review!🧻 24 Family Mega Rolls = 123 Regular Rolls 🧻“Math wizards at Charmin, we salute you! How you squished 123 regular rolls into 24 mega rolls, we'll never fathom.” Are they compressed with some secret bathroom sorcery? Did they hire an Origami master? Whatever the method, they seem to think it’s a formula for a never-ending wipe. So for those who dread the inevitable roll replacement – rejoice!💪 Ultra Strong, Like a Mini Bathroom Bodyguard 💪Nobody likes a breach, especially not whilst in the throes of personal endeavours. Charmin claims “Ultra Strong” properties, akin to a miniature bodyguard for your behind, ensuring that no unwanted entities cross the border. Respect!👑 A Touch of Luxury for Your Royal Derriere 👑Designed to be gentle on the skin yet tough on, ahem, residue, this toilet paper could very well be the unsung hero in your daily routine. It promises a ‘Clean Touch’ which is undoubtedly a nod to nobility for your nether regions. Finally, your royal behind gets the pampering it silently, yet desperately, craves.🌍 For the Love of Trees and Bees 🌳🐝Now, to address the gentle giants in the room - the trees! Charmin, oh Charmin, we adore the plushness, but our earthy hearts bleed for the trees that were sacrificed for our comfort. A moment of silence for our leafy companions, and a gentle nudge towards exploring more eco-friendly options?In the End, It’s All About the Roll:All jests and japes aside, a trip to the loo is everyone’s private performance, and Charmin’s Ultra Strong Clean Touch insists on being your steadfast stagehand, ensuring every act goes off without a hitch (or a scratch). It seeks to turn your bathroom escapades into luxurious soliloquies where your behind takes center stage, basking in a spotlight of softness and strength.However, amidst the chuckles and cheeky puns, let’s not forget our green buddies, the trees, who once stood tall and proud. Perhaps the next standing ovation will be for a TP that marries comfort and sustainability? 🌲🚽🌟Take a bow, Charmin, but the encore may just belong to the eco-warriors!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best TP out there
reviews.reviewText: Best TP out there but also the most expensive. I've tried almost every brand of TP trying to find the best but cheapest brand.If you hate TP dingle berries then this Charmin Ultra Strong is for you. Everybody knows what TP dingle berries are, it's the left over tissue on your public or butt hair. Charmin Ultra Strong never ever has this problem. Also it is so strong that you instantly use less squares. It's also pretty soft compared to other "Strong" brands. A runner up to this Charmin would be the generic Target "ultra strong" brand, however it is not nearly as soft and feels almost rough. The squares might be smaller than Charmin too as the rolls are no longer wide but skinny. But it does cost half of what Charmin costs so you get what you pay for.
